oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986; Dickens, Little Jimmy, 1920-2015; The Carter Family;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) announcing the Duke of Paducah show with Little Jimmy Dickens, Carter Family, Rita Faye, Smiley and Kitty Wilson and others at the Hillsboro Street Fair on August 26.
